## Purpose
Illustrates the 6-stage integration pipeline showing message flow from ingress through processing to observability.

## Key Components
- **Stage 1 - Firewall**: Rate limiting, size validation, schema validation (security)
- **Stage 2 - Packet Processing**: JSON-RPC parsing, parameter extraction, type validation
- **Stage 3 - Backpressure**: Semaphore-based throttling, queue management, priority scheduling
- **Stage 4 - A2A Translation**: Bidirectional adaptation between A2A and LLM formats via router
- **Stage 5 - Jidoka**: Task mapping, state synchronization, event publishing (automation)
- **Stage 6 - Receipt & Telemetry**: Build receipts, OpenTelemetry spans, metrics emission
